markdownEnumDescriptions:
Order imports by name

```php
<?php
use A;
use B\C\E;
use B\C\F\G;
use B\C\F\{H, I};
use B\C\F\J;
use B\D;
```

Order imports by name, depth-first

```php
<?php
use B\C\F\{H, I};
use B\C\F\G;
use B\C\F\J;
use B\C\E;
use B\D;
use A;
```

Do not indent heredocs

```php
<?php
function f()
{
    $a = <<<EOF
Content
EOF;
}
```

Apply line indentation to heredocs

```php
<?php
function f()
{
    $a = <<<EOF
    Content
    EOF;
}
```

pretty-php.formatting.moveComments.markdownDescription:
Move comments if necessary for correct placement of adjacent delimiters and operators

```php
<?php
// Disabled:
[
    'foo'
        // comment
        , 'bar'
];
// Enabled:
[
    'foo',
    // comment
    'bar'
];
```
